name: HUMAN LABORATORY
description:
"...Welcome To The Human Laboratory ! Where We Will Create Eternal Life In Cyber ​​World ..." 

  A voice from the computer A.I greeted us the guinea pigs who lined up enter into this strange laboratory, at that moment we looked at in amazement mixed with horror with experiments conducted by scientists here. I saw a girl in a glass tube who was staring at me stiffly, her body had been half transformed, she was alive but didn't show any expression.


 Then I suddenly thought, is there really eternal life? Is it true that by changing this body with a machine I can live forever? or even we are made in to slaves for the progress of the times, sacrificing humanity for the sake of a future.
